[{"id":835637,"node":"程序员","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1641688451","description":"<p>年前被裁。过完年就开始找，陆陆续续找了 2 周多，基本没啥好的 offer ，很多都是感觉聊得不错，就没有下文了，好焦虑啊，感觉要失业了。学历也是硬伤，高中的，虽然现在升到了本科。各位大佬救救弟弟吧。</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/835637","replies":124,"created_ts":1645509141,"created":"13:52:21","title":"2022 年 Java 找工作行情","author":"zamaojava","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/zamaojava","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/ceb241693700a4c99ec13e0320d2401d?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":835771,"node":"问与答","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1629391393","description":"这个时间节点大概是等新 MacBook air 等魔怔了。19 年出 16 寸的时候我没有买，那会刚工作确实没什么钱，舍不得买。20 年出 M1 的时候，有点钱了却又犹豫了。21 年出 M1 pro 的时候，等了这么久更动摇了。<br /><br />今年 1 月初的时候，京东买了台 MacBook air ，就想赶紧把自己想买的念头终结了，结果收到货发现屏幕有个大黑点。头脑冷静下来就退了，没有换货。期间经常下单后，又趁着没发货赶紧取消。总觉得买 mac 是自己的虚荣心作祟，因为现在手上的 win 本完全满足工作之外的学习和娱乐，我也想不到自己有什么场景会用到两台电脑。<br /><br />现在这几天突然又觉得还不如一步到位买个 mbp 14 算了，但是这让我更纠结了，我都不知道我买它的理由是什么。我不需要这台 Mac ，我也找到了工作，我也工作得还行，实在是找不到一个让自己买的理由。<br /><br />想问问那些没买、想买、没想法的人，都是怎么的想法呢？","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/835771","replies":115,"created_ts":1645538599,"created":"22:03:19","title":"“我”真的需要一台 Mac 吗？","author":"rsonghao","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/rsonghao","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/7b27f5f6f912d3f1542c0497760b1917?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":835685,"node":"职场话题","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/career","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/4ea0/6fbc/770_mini.png?m=1643602261","description":"<p>不管是否真实，事实上公司里面 35 岁以上或者左右的程序员确实很少（除了嵌入式）。\n所以，咱们 35+的程序们是都转去当管理了吗？有没有大佬愿意吱个声，咱们 35+的出处在哪里，还能继续做技术吗？</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/835685","replies":106,"created_ts":1645517546,"created":"16:12:26","title":"35 岁+的程序员都去哪里了？","author":"loheng","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/loheng","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/ca3f00833294e9442023a69716dbedcb?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":835651,"node":"程序员","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1641688451","description":"<ul>\n<li>大二学弟刚面完腾讯，热乎</li>\n<li>2022 年，进大厂要趁早</li>\n<li>今年跳槽的可以再等等</li>\n</ul>\n<p>还有这个</p>\n<ul>\n<li>29 岁程序员，1 月无情被辞</li>\n</ul>\n<p>这都什么标题 哈哈哈 最近广告文有点太多了。</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/835651","replies":106,"created_ts":1645510798,"created":"14:19:58","title":"那个敖丙 微信公众号简介是三太子敖丙的号发的文章标题有点那啥","author":"xx19941215","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/xx19941215","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/6bb65cf94df8d155c76d8634691360b4?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":835762,"node":"Vim","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/vim","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/077e/29b1/249_mini.png?m=1592121370","description":"<p>看报道 Sven 不仅是 VIM 之父 Bram 的好友，也为 Vim 的推广做出了重大贡献，甚至 Vim 的官方主页 <a href=\"http://vim.org\" rel=\"nofollow\">vim.org</a> 也是他注册的。</p>\n<p>致敬</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/835762","replies":91,"created_ts":1645535353,"created":"21:09:13","title":"Vim 的主要维护者之一 Sven Guckes 去世了","author":"yuhangch","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/yuhangch","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/0cc7/3790/467934_mini.png?m=1637808396"},{"id":835597,"node":"广州","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/guangzhou","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/98f1/3708/20_mini.png?m=1542423096","description":"<p>坐标在广州，最近看到关于买房首付降到二成的新闻，然后又看到了广州的贷款利率下降的新闻。\n想请教一下各位的看法，对类似广州增城，南沙这种离市区较远，只适合预算不高的刚需的地区的房价怎么看</p>\n<p>家里人想催促买房，但是我觉得类似于降低贷款利率的政策可能以后还会持续推出，government 不会让房价上涨的太多，房价在以后相当长的时间内都是会平稳，刚需等的时间越长，就越有可能等到更加优惠的政策，从而可能买到更好的房子。各位怎么看</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/835597","replies":83,"created_ts":1645500655,"created":"11:30:55","title":"首付降低，利率下降，刚需是现在买房还是等？","author":"banjueaz","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/banjueaz","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/bff85ad11f56f06a663e572b24bede4b?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":835585,"node":"宽带症候群","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/bb","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a3c6/5c29/108_mini.png?m=1635654723","description":"<div class=\"embedded_video_wrapper\"><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/iyQjjgOfPnQ\" class=\"embedded_video\" allowfullscreen=\"\" type=\"text/html\" id=\"ytplayer\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe></div><br />如视频所示，方法是否可行。。。","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/835585","replies":79,"created_ts":1645499031,"created":"11:03:51","title":"可不可以用树莓派作为旁路由从而实现在电视上看 Youtube?","author":"Ashore","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/Ashore","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/d300/d7f2/568178_mini.png?m=1645498910"},{"id":835579,"node":"健康","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/fit","node_image":"/static/img/node_default_mini.png","description":"<p>来深圳三年半，最大的变化就是体重增加了 20+斤，上周末去体检，显示体重已经是偏胖了 -_-. 是时候把心心念念的健身给提上日程了。</p>\n<p>主要目的就是 <strong>减重</strong> 和 <strong>减脂</strong>。由于梨形身材加工作久坐，胖起来的脂肪大部分体现在肚子和大腿上，所以减肥的重点部位是<strong>肚子</strong>和<strong>大腿</strong>。</p>\n<p>作为一个健身小白，想请教一下健身经验丰富的 V 友们：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>健身新人需要找个私教入门吗？</li>\n<li>如果不需要私教，有什么建议的项目？</li>\n<li>保持运动量的情况下，正常饮食是否可行？(不想节食)</li>\n<li>健身达人的你有什么其他建议？</li>\n</ol>\n<p><a href=\"https://imgtu.com/i/HxbYpd\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"HxbYpd.jpg\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://s4.ax1x.com/2022/02/22/HxbYpd.jpg\"/></a></p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/835579","replies":73,"created_ts":1645498156,"created":"10:49:16","title":"体检显示偏胖了，有什么健身减肥的建议？","author":"devilte","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/devilte","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/e5ef/96d1/527498_mini.png?m=1640245187"},{"id":835688,"node":"程序员","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1641688451","description":"<p>搞了个 X86 ，打算拿来 7x24 开机，主要装 homeassistant ，node ，web 这些常用环境，需要使用到 Docker ，</p>\n<p>刚开始打算的是 ESXI 装 Ubuntu 再套 Docker</p>\n<p>但是想了下，我又不拿来玩软路由，所有的环境在 Linux 下就都能跑了，直接物理机上个 Linux 就行哇，是不是没必要走 ESXI 这样套个娃（主要还是考虑是不是有性能损耗，虽然我这些东西好像对性能也没啥过分的要求，哈哈）</p>\n<p>求大佬分析下利弊，有必要套娃吗？</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/835688","replies":72,"created_ts":1645518289,"created":"16:24:49","title":"问一下大佬，家用服务器是选择 ESXI 套娃，还是直接物理机上 Linux","author":"v2410117","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/v2410117","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/5b9c/3f2f/286407_mini.png?m=1516860734"},{"id":835641,"node":"程序员","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1641688451","description":"企业微信更新了，内嵌了个傻逼的浏览器，贼他么恶心，群里发的链接默认全都是内嵌浏览器打开，还不能更改为使用系统浏览器。 <br />结果导致内部系统，办公系统 OA 都要重新登录，有一些链接带 cookie 的，根本就打不开了。以前点一次就可以打开链接的，现在要点两下才能使用系统浏览器打开。这产品经理脑袋有泡吧，我看下次直接装个 OS 到企业微信得了。<br />好了，我喷完了","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/835641","replies":70,"created_ts":1645509415,"created":"13:56:55","title":"腾讯企业微信的产品经理用脚想需求吗？","author":"oldboy627","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/oldboy627","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/0dc3b2473c7162bd5da34aa0682219a9?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":835572,"node":"职场话题","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/career","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/4ea0/6fbc/770_mini.png?m=1643602261","description":"<p>大家最晚什么时间公司发年终奖？</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/835572","replies":70,"created_ts":1645497657,"created":"10:40:57","title":"4 月底才发年终奖","author":"461da73c","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/461da73c","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/959f9561c0f7c1ef7217d0ba34169976?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":835565,"node":"分享创造","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/create","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/70ef/df2e/17_mini.png?m=1629391403","description":"<p>过年回老家，亲朋好友来家里串门，询问 WiFi 密码，发现不记得 WiFi 密码了，父母家，岳父母家，自己家的密码都忘记了，只有登上路由改密码，报密码的时候还要和对方反复确认，就很烦，干脆最后几天假期在家怒肝代码，写了一个管理 WiFi 密码和通过二维码分享 WiFi 的工具“WiFi 分享管家”。</p>\n<p>APP 地址：  <a href=\"https://apps.apple.com/cn/app/id1610131321\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://apps.apple.com/cn/app/id1610131321</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://imgtg.com/image/UEf1Y\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"UEf1Y.jpg\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://i.w3tt.com/2022/02/22/UEf1Y.jpg\"/></a>\n<a href=\"https://imgtg.com/image/UElHv\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"UElHv.jpg\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://i.w3tt.com/2022/02/22/UElHv.jpg\"/></a></p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/835565","replies":62,"created_ts":1645496267,"created":"10:17:47","title":"过年回老家，亲朋好友来串门使用 WiFi 太麻烦，写了一个 WiFi 管理和分享的小工具，欢迎大家使用","author":"letuslinux","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/letuslinux","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/52c9/da64/60350_mini.png?m=1609689454"},{"id":835537,"node":"问与答","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1629391393","description":"每天晚上入睡后，都会做梦，感觉是做完一个梦再来一个。早上闹铃响的时候，还在梦里，然后一响被打断就醒了","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/835537","replies":57,"created_ts":1645487756,"created":"07:55:56","title":"每日一梦是什么感受","author":"junziyangyang","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/junziyangyang","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/e129114ccf3629232d8831e0941354a7?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":835619,"node":"Kubernetes","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/k8s","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/27ed/0fb9/1039_mini.png?m=1601353687","description":"<p>换个角度，新人还有必要从 docker 开始学吗？</p>\n<p>感觉不如直接 podman 或者 containerd 算了？</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/835619","replies":48,"created_ts":1645506168,"created":"13:02:48","title":"k8s 抛弃 docker 之后， docker 还有前途吗？","author":"julyclyde","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/julyclyde","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/ac0f68b04756cb56a94d5e48805a34e6?s=24&d=retro"}]